Source code for 3rd party libraries

      The Connector for SharePoint uses various 3rd party open source
      libraries. The versions of these libraries are embedded in the
      names of the files. If you have trouble locating the source code
      of any of the libraries used by the Connector for SharePoint,
      you can file an issue on this project site.
